      • getCredentialsFromVcap

        public static CredentialUtils.ServiceCredentials getCredentialsFromVcap(String serviceName)
        Calls methods to parse VCAP_SERVICES and retrieve credential values. For some values, if VCAP_SERVICES aren't present, it'll fall back to checking JNDI.
        Parameters:
        serviceName - the service name
        Returns:
        ServiceCredentials object containing parsed values

      • getVcapValue

        public static String getVcapValue(String serviceName,
                  String key,
                  String plan)
        Returns the value associated with the provided key from the VCAP_SERVICES, or null if it doesn't exist. In the case of the API URL, if VCAP_SERVICES aren't present, this method will also search in JNDI.
        Parameters:
        serviceName - the service name
        key - the key whose value should be returned
        plan - the plan name
        Returns:
        the value of the provided key
